    bibo:volume "2554" ;
    dc:creator "De, Gilberto J.; Narita, João P. Z." ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "Description of a new species of Neocypholaelaps (Acari: Ameroseiidae) from Brazil, with a key to the world species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196879>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196880> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196879>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Neocypholaelaps geonamae n. sp. Female. A. Lateral view of chelicera; B. Variations of epistome; C. Ventral view of gnathosoma; D. Dorsal view of idiosoma; E. Detail of tritosternum; F. Ventral view of idiosoma; G. Right peritreme and associated shields (a = dorsal shield; b = peritrematal shield; c = exopodal shield; d = striated unsclerotised cuticle between peritreme and exopodal shield); H. Spermathecal apparatus; I. Pre-tarsus I. Scales in micrometres. Pores and lyrifissures enlarged to allow their differentiation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196879/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196880>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Neocypholaelaps geonamae n. sp. Male. A. Lateral view of chelicera; B. Variation of the lateral view of spermatodactyl; C. Dorso-ventral view of spermatodactyl; D. Variation of pilus dentilis; E. Dorsal view of idiosoma; F. Ventral view of idiosoma. Scales in micrometres. Pores and lyrifissures enlarged to allow their differentiation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196880/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

